<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Ssh Key on baby steps coding journey</title><link>https://aya222222.github.io/tags/ssh-key/</link><description>Recent content in Ssh Key on baby steps coding journey</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 21:18:09 -0400</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://aya222222.github.io/tags/ssh-key/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>SSH Key: How To Solve Permissions 0644 for 'file.pub' are too open</title><link>https://aya222222.github.io/p/ssh-key-how-to-solve-permissions-0644-for-file.pub-are-too-open/</link><pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 21:18:09 -0400</pubDate><guid>https://aya222222.github.io/p/ssh-key-how-to-solve-permissions-0644-for-file.pub-are-too-open/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;br>&lt;br>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I wrote the host infomation to ./ssh/config:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Host arbitrary-name
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> HostName 133.125.85.79
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> User user-name
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> IdentityFile location-of-secret-key
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>But I got this error:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Permissions 0644 for &amp;#39;secret-key.pub&amp;#39; are too open.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">It is required that your private key files are NOT accessible by others.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">This private key will be ignored.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>To fix this, I run this command on terminal.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">chmod 400 ~/.ssh/secret-key
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>And after run this command, it works!&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>